org.apache.fineract.organisation.teller.domain

Class Cashier

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.data.jpa.domain.AbstractPersistable<java.lang.Long>
      • org.apache.fineract.organisation.teller.domain.Cashier
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, org.springframework.data.domain.Persistable<java.lang.Long>

    @Entity
public class Cashier
extends org.springframework.data.jpa.domain.AbstractPersistable<java.lang.Long>
    Provides the base model for a cashier. Represents a row in the "m_cashiers" database table, with each column mapped to a property of this class.
    Since:
    2.0.0
    Author:
    Markus Geiss
